<U+041E><U+0434><U+043D><U+0435><U+0441><U+0435> <U+0438><U+0445> <U+0441><U+0432><U+043E><U+0458><U+043E><U+0458> <U+0441><U+0442><U+0430><U+0440><U+043E><U+0458> <U+043C><U+0430><U+0458><U+0446><U+0438>:<br/>
"<U+0422><U+043E> <U+0441><U+0430><U+043C> <U+0442><U+0435><U+0431><U+0435> <U+0434><U+0430><U+043D><U+0430><U+0441> <U+0438><U+0437><U+043E><U+0440><U+0430><U+043E>."<ref>Karad<U+017E>i<U+0107> 2000, "[http://www.rastko.rs/knjizevnost/usmena/vkaradzic-pesme_II_c.html#_Toc494261518 <U+041E><U+0440><U+0430><U+045A><U+0435> <U+041C><U+0430><U+0440><U+043A><U+0430> <U+041A><U+0440><U+0430><U+0459><U+0435><U+0432><U+0438><U+045B><U+0430>]".</ref>
